    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 1 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}I'm not gonna waste a single minute![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
